#: ''You can expand this compact umbrella to cover a large table.''
#<!--VTrDecompose--> {{algebra}} To rewrite an expression as an equivalent sum of terms.
#: ''Use the binomial theorem to expand <math>{(x+1)}^4</math> to <math>x^4 + 4x^3 + 6x^2 + 4x + 1</math>''

